Package: x11typewrite
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Description: distraction-free typewriter-style text editor for X11
 Typewrite OS is a minimal, typewriter-inspired writing environment.
 This package provides the X11/Cairo client (binary name: x11typewrite).
 Features include multi-page documents, PDF export, font and theme
 selection, and optional letter-style margins.
